flicker_cursor;Senya;
add_portrait;Senya;Left;
speak;Senya;Too old... what a load of crap|Anyone can tell that old man can move better than all of us.|Is this some form of test?
remove_portrait;Senya;
flicker_cursor;Schuri;
add_portrait;Schuri;Left
speak;Schuri;That man...He's radiating magic.|What in the world was that magic he used...
remove_portrait;Schuri
end_skip;
flicker_cursor;MC;
add_portrait;MC;Right;
speak;Aesc;Boy, Why are you using a regular lance here?
speak;MC;Wh-
mirror_portrait;MC;
mirror_portrait;MC;
speak;Aesc;I'm usually telepathy boy.|I'm still in the tavern|Has That Cyrus not taught you anything?
speak;MC;...Not really. I'm magically inept. I can only use healing magic.|I learned to use a sword and spear to protect my friends.
speak;Aesc;...?|Is that why you have a battle staff?|
speak;MC;I don't know why but I have to take the crystal out of healing staves|then move it to my staff.
speak;Aesc;That's old magic boy.|You're channeling the crystal's magic to perform old magics.
speak;MC;huh?
speak;Aesc;Old magics! Light? Dark?|Did Cyrus teach you nothing about it?|
speak;MC;I mean we were told that magic exists in a triangle but nowadays...|I thought light and dark magic is impractical?
speak;Aesc;...No I suspect he was worried about something else...|Listen boy. Light magic is highly potent to monsters.|You harness positive emotions and channel it outwards.|...I'll teach you dark magic later perhaps.|I'm going to warp a basic light tome to your hands|I'll try to guide you through this.
give_wexp;MC;Light (Light);30
give_item;MC;Lightning (Lightning)
